# Changelog

## [0.5.0] - 2025-01-XX

### Added
- Video upload and library management
- Interactive timeline with zoom and scrubbing
- Real-time canvas preview
- Properties panel with transform, effects, and audio controls
- Export simulation with progress tracking
- Undo/redo system with keyboard shortcuts
- Responsive design for all screen sizes

### Technical
- React 18 + TypeScript implementation
- Tailwind CSS design system
- Radix UI component library
- HTML5 video processing
